        <infon key="n">4</infon>
        <offset>411</offset>
        <text>We present evidence for a third response: resistance.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">5</infon>
        <offset>465</offset>
        <text>We examined microbial community response to perturbation caused by nutrient enrichment in salt marsh sediments using deep pyrosequencing of 16S rRNA and functional gene microarrays targeting the nirS gene.
</text>
