      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">6</infon>
        <offset>671</offset>
        <text>Composition of the microbial community, as demonstrated by both genes, was unaffected by significant variations in external nutrient supply in our sampling locations, despite demonstrable and diverse nutrient-induced changes in many aspects of marsh ecology.
</text>
